Subject: [PATCH v7 07/16] ufs: core: mcq: Calculate queue depth
Date:   Tue, 29 Nov 2022 10:53:13 -0800
Message-ID: <9497b4a0f72e8cbc712e328d1f9ae38635eb2284.1669747235.git.quic_asutoshd@quicinc.com>
